/>\nbtw天竺鼠係群居動物，最好兩隻或以上一齊養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6e7d28f66ffb740c82bda32bc6fb19c6521611","tid":185133,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"我都有養緊2隻，佢地真係好細膽嫁。<br />\n屎尿都比較多。。"},{"pid":"f878384398a6e68583b3a74a2e9bc338d6551319","tid":185133,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾個禮拜都有惗過養小天<br />\n但最後因緣際會下決定左養刺蝟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw天竺鼠係群居動物，最好兩隻或以上一齊養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係未必，我本來都以為係咁<br />\n所以先養埋第二隻。<br />\n不過發現第一隻好似鐘意一隻鼠on99咁"},{"pid":"8e127faa0cd4cceecb754e92b9330fd1d7049ded","tid":185133,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l9wzjxvo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl9wzjxvo&h=4efce282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剪指甲真係好難"},{"pid":"37a61687d8b218f05ae200f9e14fb8b35c30a58d","tid":185133,"uid":36206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"玄裝三藏"},{"pid":"0265757b51623df950cc96eac2b5857779cece24","tid":185133,"uid":5987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"老鼠"},{"pid":"9396af08b7cae2b9d53da9b2f1132440e89a75f7","tid":185133,"uid":57129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"好得意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8954f28ac0f8bc65049e798db1bf06eec606b955","tid":185133,"uid":99484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"好得意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會叫？"},{"pid":"b5884e10539f47cf8e74cbd46c0b815c8ba9ec0a","tid":185133,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾個禮拜都有惗過養小天<br />\n但最後因緣際會下決定左養刺蝟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw天竺鼠係群居動物，最好兩隻或以上一齊養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係未必，我本來都以為係咁<br />\n所以先養埋第二隻。<br />\n不過發現第一隻好似鐘意一隻鼠on99咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就係因為唔想養兩隻先放棄養天竺鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3148c2e37106b5d4ca0e6f259e1ce36f50937011","tid":185133,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"三藏"},{"pid":"e1a331ce0c6964ef19db45770245de2b16798477","tid":185133,"uid":27397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:04:32.000Z","msg":"印度感情咖哩"},{"pid":"4d0a7ecd8687a48d4c7b3f302531e4ec2afd8079","tid":185133,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"51515151"},{"pid":"ccb79ff056c1a8a7bc2258fd4bbc87161eac1a9f","tid":185133,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早幾個禮拜都有惗過養小天<br />\n但最後因緣際會下決定左養刺蝟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw天竺鼠係群居動物，最好兩隻或以上一齊養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係未必，我本來都以為係咁<br />\n所以先養埋第二隻。<br />\n不過發現第一隻好似鐘意一隻鼠on99咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就係因為唔想養兩隻先放棄養天竺鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇番d群組，原來某部份可能係毒撚格。<br />\n天竺鼠每隻都唔同，只不過佢地性格純，好容易就可以合籠先令人覺得一定要養二隻。"},{"pid":"d6a936b578570490431e55189fec238bea6f3921","tid":185133,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好得意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會叫？</blockquote><br />\n我自己果2隻會，開心會叫，唔高興又會叫，不過有太多種叫聲...一般最熟識都應該係515151同埋咕咕咕"},{"pid":"36fd6380ab3bafe8fb9dde03d9d9aca65b41a8d4","tid":185133,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早幾個禮拜都有惗過養小天<br />\n但最後因緣際會下決定左養刺蝟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw天竺鼠係群居動物，最好兩隻或以上一齊養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係未必，我本來都以為係咁<br />\n所以先養埋第二隻。<br />\n不過發現第一隻好似鐘意一隻鼠on99咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就係因為唔想養兩隻先放棄養天竺鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇番d群組，原來某部份可能係毒撚格。<br />\n天竺鼠每隻都唔同，只不過佢地性格純，好容易就可以合籠先令人覺得一定要養二隻。</blockquote><br />\n但我睇外國既群組都話係herd animals...係天性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過性格呢家野都係睇緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇黎我暫時冇緣<br />\n唔排除幾年後會養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349560bea422eb29df892952b65c669898032e85","tid":185133,"uid":78988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"美芬"},{"pid":"a196f8dd47b3f3de8804913e07ad75f0906895fe","tid":185133,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:39:46.000Z","msg":"豆豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55814f5b0ed220b337d0332e1e00971d68a75681","tid":185133,"uid":6747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早幾個禮拜都有惗過養小天<br />\n但最後因緣際會下決定左養刺蝟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw天竺鼠係群居動物，最好兩隻或以上一齊養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實真係未必，我本來都以為係咁<br />\n所以先養埋第二隻。<br />\n不過發現第一